    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294340/extras/8ce2a48ef5ddfac7357d6c751561d8f9.avif?t=1727715867\" width=616 height=158 /></span><br><br>《媛红》以二十世纪 20 年代平行时空中的朝鲜为背景，其中，年轻的遇害女主角将重返生者的世界，并对罪魁祸首实行报复。这位少女与身为死神的阴间使者达成了交易，从而获得了附身并操控生者的能力。而作为交换条件，她必须达成死难同胞的遗愿，并为他们的灵魂求得安息。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294340/extras/3da1aec72977320c8412fc4e4f54bb2c.avif?t=1727715867\" width=616 height=185 /></span><br> <br>这位少女能从生物身上摄取生命力（气），变成幽灵并占据他们的身体，以便开展复仇行动。她要借屠夫之手伸张正义。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294340/extras/a4e3db7d73e4d84c0fe73736078f8eba.poster.avif?t=1727715867\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294340/extras/a4e3db7d73e4d84c0fe73736078f8eba.webm?t=1727715867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294340/extras/a4e3db7d73e4d84c0fe73736078f8eba.mp4?t=1727715867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>女主角将直面各种创伤。面对冷酷的敌人，少女容不得犯错，所以，她必须耐心等待攻击时机的到来。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294340/extras/654970d335a2b98cdf5bd8d11317c7c1.poster.avif?t=1727715867\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294340/extras/654970d335a2b98cdf5bd8d11317c7c1.webm?t=1727715867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294340/extras/654970d335a2b98cdf5bd8d11317c7c1.mp4?t=1727715867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>她将潜入军事基地，占据毫无防备的敌人的身体，并尽力在与入侵者的斗争中占据上风。请帮助她在隐迹潜踪和大开杀戒之间找到平衡，同时实施残酷的复仇行动。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294340/extras/9eb43465aea1f82d3468358d7fefef56.poster.avif?t=1727715867\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294340/extras/9eb43465aea1f82d3468358d7fefef56.webm?t=1727715867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294340/extras/9eb43465aea1f82d3468358d7fefef56.mp4?t=1727715867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
